            "href": "https://www.wandisco.com"
          }}>{`Contact WANdisco`}</a>{` for a license that will meet your migration needs.`}</p></div></div>
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "option-1-command-line-operation"
    }}>{`Option 1: Command line operation`}</h3>
    <p>{`Download the `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`live-migrator.jar`}</inlineCode>{` file, then as the `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`hdfs`}</inlineCode>{` user on a cluster edge node, execute`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{}}>{`$ hadoop jar live-migrator.jar
`}</code></pre>
    <p>{`to start LiveData Migrator and view the action prompt:`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{}}>{`
