   ###### ###### ###      &&&    &&&    &&      && &&     &&  &      &   &        &  &       &       &
     ##     ##   ##        &&    &&      &&&&&& && &&     &&  &&&&&&\`    &  &&&&&&    &&&&&   \`&&&&&\`


 WANdisco LiveMigrator


  Welcome to WANdisco LiveMigrator
  - Type "help" for assistance, <TAB> for completion.

Please type \`help\` to see available commands
WANdisco LiveData Migrator >>
`}</code></pre>
    <h4 {...{
      "id": "defining-a-source"
    }}>{`Defining a source`}</h4>
    <div {...{
      "className": "admonition admonition-note alert alert--secondary"
    }}><div parentName="div" {...{
        "className": "admonition-heading"
      }}><h5 parentName="div"><span parentName="h5" {...{
